	<h1 class="title">沃尔玛在中国的一大笔股权被卖了，这超市还做得起来吗？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/3926/small/3926.jpg?1421980719" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">费丽婷 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-10 14:04:07 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15900/medium/15900.jpg?1444455472" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="15900" data-title="《沃尔玛在中国的一大笔股权被卖了，这超市还做得起来吗？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/15900/medium/15900.jpg?1444455472" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/15900.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
